{"tid":1839522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我見武漢咁慘，大家可唔可以幫我spread呢段嘢出去，我想打救大陸同胞","createTime":"2020-01-24T12:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T12:57:42.000Z","uid":315785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"450c9a2c77e4996daa095321bbfda4b242e99fb8","tid":1839522,"uid":315785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"幫下手推得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我喺共青團講唔到野，唔該丫，呢幾晚我都訓唔著.....<br />\n<br />\n终于忍不住要说了，大家好我是香港的，请放心，我不是黄尸暴徒，看到内地同胞难受成这样，我特别心疼。大家听着这个方法或许有效的抑制肺炎跟发热，我表哥是香港药剂师，他说有一种药名叫acetaminophen乙酰胺酚，是退烧药，除了退烧，吃高一点的分量还可以消炎，原理是acetaminophen可以抑制环氧合酶，减轻肺部发炎状况。这种药呢，网上说一下子最多能吃8克，但我表哥说8克其实是很安全的，因为要防止有人吃多了才把安全的剂量降低，至少要11克才有副作用，他还说有几个病人2小时内吃了15颗500mg的acetaminophen就没事了，不过现在还在观察中。把这个方法传出去!香港的药剂师应该是可信的，不过香港的废青暴徒们就是不说!"},{"pid":"d58b466c2fac8526b72d70423743e47dd4ae572b","tid":1839522,"uid":315785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推唔到啊..."},{"pid":"b48ee898004db2be99cfc09d85d19fccb0447fcb","tid":1839522,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6edbc958de891310888f3dbb8d21d2821674691","tid":1839522,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"好東西 要分享"},{"pid":"a01d1206c4f8bbbab3ea92314a5b5c14655cfe44","tid":1839522,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:52:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"bcd7d8e693cf5939c07b4353e628cf4b9de7d416","tid":1839522,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"再推"}]}